4f85fc3d204a6fd390323","tid":2210901,"uid":343798,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T20:30:11.000Z","msg":"認真答 （雖然上網都搵到大把人講）<br />\n<br />\n有budget就真心買晒兩部 冇錢要二揀一就睇你用嚟做咩 <br />\n<br />\n如果你要specific software就一定用MacBook <br />\n<br />\n如果普通用家用嚟主要睇吓Netflix YouTube +prefer手寫notes+普通文書 嘅就iPad pro幾好<br />\n<br />\n我自己淨用 iPad Pro最大缺點就<br />\n1. Microsoft office 垃圾到仆街 尤其是Excel(Microsoft 問題 死症，不過好似話會update）<br />\n2. 我淨用iPad pro要買keyboard case，magic keyboard貴 想take notes要拆部iPad出嚟有啲麻煩<br />\n但用Logitech嗰個又同mba 差唔多重+好厚<br />\n3. 用zoom冇得show 樣+take notes 同時做，就算split screen 都唔得 係zoom問題冇得解<br />\n4. 好多app用落先發覺同laptop比少好多feature, 例如Spotify iPad 版同laptop版冇得比/ 上面講嘅Microsoft, etc<br />\n4. 其實買iPad pro+pencil+keyboard 都差唔多/貴過mba，真係睇你使用習慣係咩<br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得iPad 最大賣點真係支筆+開機快唔使煩<br />\n但其他嘢用laptop做會爽啲快啲 <br />\n<br />\n我文科仔打篇文 做research 整ppt用laptop快好多 <br />\n讀business 要用excel可以直接買laptop<br />\n<br />\n不過 真係冇錢就買普通laptop 啦 除非你好鍾意用筆take notes啫<br />\n如果入咗apple 個ecosystem就shut up and take my money買晒佢啦 <br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多，諗到再加<br />\n希望你買完用得開心唔會後悔<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2ac75803a7876c3e4696224f9b3636f887a397","tid":2210901,"uid":87039,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T23:22:12.000Z","msg":"有desktop就買iPad pro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無desktop就買MacBook <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc985f142214482bdff0990e545392b60b7b276","tid":2210901,"uid":38540,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T23:25:21.000Z","msg":"ipad pro<br />\n<br />\nshowoff用<br />\n<br />\n反正你都唔係用黎讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3676dbc7f85f869c9fd51ea35060046f23b726df","tid":2210901,"uid":363363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T23:26:22.000Z","msg":"兩部買哂囉 用緊MBA <br />\n而家想買部iPad Air jot notes<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e94ed320c82629c75a9b0d77af5f21bc5e8015d","tid":2210901,"uid":123296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T23:28:05.000Z","msg":"認真答<br />\n齋睇notes 簡單文書 咁就ipad pro + apple pencil + keyboard(optional)<br />\n要用其他software macbook"},{"pid":"55cfa04e07798cc6f03799b773f425426f9b0634","tid":2210901,"uid":50759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T23:28:53.000Z","msg":"錢少的話，點解唔用普通laptop?<br />\n如果為左支筆，你都係pro"},{"pid":"2ea876570783a437712c78a925f9c0a429cd03fe","tid":2210901,"uid":367408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0645bcc69963167aece15b1c7b8a41240c6cd14d","tid":2210901,"uid":51171,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T18:37:00.000Z","msg":"唔知ipad pro同mba有咩分別???!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑撚左<br />\n唔好咁啦屌你老母<br />\n上到u問條問題都咁撚on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T23:36:23.000Z","msg":"你又知係U?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be331b52c19be2d4f3370012a059c19ee766d9c9","tid":2210901,"uid":372221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6f2e11906963fee2a6ea6065872d44c61e4f08b6","tid":2210901,"uid":376638,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"91e3e2b45f85a3e71b21ab69a452642d3e602b4c","tid":2210901,"uid":146934,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T18:33:42.000Z","msg":"用apple唔用pro系列會比人笑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T19:12:31.000Z","msg":"小弟頗窮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T00:05:42.000Z","msg":"唔好買囉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9fe6326e15f57713735ee1622bb8b60a6ef7d27","tid":2210901,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T00:26:07.000Z","msg":"如果要drop note 記住買apple care"},{"pid":"aa8feb9842cdf790a28094004232a